NOTES for your presentation and slides:

 

·         Do not provide any internal emails to customers to contact you. All questions should be directed to the discussion forums on Connect.

·         Use the attached template and format

·         Do not forward the internal S+ to customers – this breaks confidentiality

·         Do not set your Lync to DND as I cannot contact you prior or during the presentation or add me as a contact that can interrupt a DND status

·         Please leave all moderation during the session to me

·         Don’t discuss any dates

·         Do not answer questions in the IM window

 

·         Set your screen resolution for demos to 1024 x 768 for best viewing for participants
